snippet.title: 3D Monters Surgery Game, Operation Game - Kids Board Game Review and Play
snippet.description:
With this Monster Surgery Game you must operate carefully, otherwise the monster will shake suddenly! The monster is lying on the operation bed and there are 11 pieces of body parts inside the monster’s body. Players operate carefully using pair of tweezers to pick up the parts from the monster’s body without the monster trembling.

For a challenging game involving hand eye coordination and manual dexterity, then Monster Surgery from Spears Games will provide a challenge for your little one. Your child has to remove parts and organs from a Frankenstein type monster with a pair of tweezers. If they touch the metal at the bottom, the monster vibrates frantically.
You spin the wheel and whichever part the arrow points to is the part that you have to remove.
Different points are awarded to different parts according to difficulty, the winner is the one who has most points at the end of the game
For 2 - 4 players
Assembled Dimensions: 8L x 5.8W x 25H cm
Contents: A game board with a pair of tweezers and 11 Body-parts
Batteries required: 2 AA batteries (not included)
Suitable for ages: 4+ years.
